ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of FILOMENA FRISINA of Toronto, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Lisa M.
